properties.Name: CreditRatingAgency
properties.Description:
An independent third-party agency that investigates risk associated with holding a financial instrument, or a Customer/Applicant credit history.

Ex:
-  Moody's Investor Service
-  Standard & Poor's
-  Duff & Phelps
-  Fitch Investors Service
-  Bloomberg
-  STN Money Markets
-  Reuters
-  Telerate
-  TRW Information Services
-  Trans Union Credit Information Company
-  CSC/Equifax
-  Dun & Bradstreet
-  Equifax
-  Experian
-  Internal

Columns.Name: CreditRatingAgencyId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Credit Rating Agency.

Columns.Name: CreditRatingAgencyName
Columns.Description: The business name of the Credit Rating Agency.

Columns.Name: CreditRatingAgencyDescription
Columns.Description: The description of the Credit Rating Agency.

Columns.Name: LocationId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Location.

Columns.Name: FaxNumber
Columns.Description: The fax number of the Credit Rating Agency

Columns.Name: TelephoneNumber
Columns.Description: The telephone number of the Credit Rating Agency

Columns.Name: PrimaryContactName
Columns.Description: The name of the primary contact for the reviewer at the Credit Rating Agency.

Columns.Name: AlternateContactName
Columns.Description: The name of the alternate contact at the Credit Rating Agency.

Columns.Name: PartyId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Party.
